com.interpss.opf

Interface BaseOpfBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBus, BaseAclfBus<AclfGen,AclfLoad>, Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DclfOpfBus, DclfOpfGenBus, OpfBus, OpfGenBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfGenBusImpl, OpfBusImpl, OpfGenBusImpl

    public interface BaseOpfBus
extends AclfBus
    A representation of the model object 'Base Opf Bus'. OPF base Bus class for OPF analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • LMP
    • PL Inequ Multiplier
    • PU Inequ Multiplier
    • QL Inequ Multiplier
    • QU Inequ Multiplier
    See Also:
    OpfPackage.getBaseOpfBus()
